name: $page
desc: This is a page that represents a human readable rendering of an example.

name: $example
desc: This is a page that represents a list of resources of one or more types.

desc: This is a page showing where an included guide is injected.

desc: This is a page that represents a presented resource. This is typically used for generated conformance resource presentations.
